<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">Discord Calendar Bot</span>
    <h1>Discord calendar bot for events, RSVPs, reminders, and Google Calendar sync</h1>
    <p>Soren turns your Discord server into a working community calendar with slash-command event creation, live RSVP buttons, recurring schedules, waitlists, reminders, and optional Google Calendar integrations.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-4);justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--space-6);">
      <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" class="btn btn--primary btn--large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Add Soren to Discord</a>
      <a href="/setup" class="btn btn--secondary btn--large">Read the setup guide</a>
