      <p>Soren fits gaming clans, guilds, community groups, creator communities, study groups, project teams, and any server where people need to coordinate around real times.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3 reveal">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Gaming clans and guilds</h4>
        <p>Schedule raids, scrims, practice nights, tournaments, and recurring weekly sessions with RSVP caps and reminders.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Community servers</h4>
        <p>Plan watch parties, workshops, meetings, voice events, office hours, and member-led meetups from one Discord calendar bot.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Teams and clubs</h4>
        <p>Keep volunteer shifts, project calls, club meetings, and shared calendars visible inside the channels members already use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</span>
      <h2>Discord calendar bot questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" type="button"><span>What is a Discord calendar bot?</span><span class="faq-chevron">▾</span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer">A Discord calendar bot lets a server create, publish, remind, and manage events directly in Discord channels. Soren adds RSVP buttons, recurrence, role reminders, Google Calendar sync, waitlists, and event exports.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" type="button"><span>Can Soren sync Discord events with Google Calendar?</span><span class="faq-chevron">▾</span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Soren can connect Google Calendar integrations, post weekly digest summaries into Discord channels, and export upcoming Discord events as calendar files.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" type="button"><span>Does Soren support recurring events?</span><span class="faq-chevron">▾</span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Soren supports daily, weekly, bi-weekly, bi-monthly, monthly, and custom recurring Discord events.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" type="button"><span>How fast can I set it up?</span><span class="faq-chevron">▾</span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer">Most servers can add Soren, run <code>/setup</code>, assign an Event Creator role, and publish the first event in a few minutes.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

